      <title>Nickel 28 与被解雇的首席执行官达成和解，结束不当行为索赔</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/nickel-28-and-fired-ceo-reach-settlement-to-end-misconduct-claim</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Nickel 28 Capital Corp. 的前首席执行官同意放弃其所持有的该公司近一半股份，该公司指控他和其他被罢免的高管“严重不当行为”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/nickel-28-and-fired-ceo-reach-settlement-to-end-misconduct-claim</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 19:39:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
